\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1 \xt Mt 13.1-2; Mk 3.9-10\x* B…®sap k…®ndakon Yesu Genesaret\f * \fr 5:1 \ft Genesaret uŇčun Galili Pakbi ∆ódap dakon mani k…®nda.\f* Pakbi ∆ódap …®leŇč…®kon agek PiŇčkop dakon gen yaŇčakwan am…®n morapm…® da ab…®Ňč uŇčun da kapmatsisok aŇčgwas…®Ňček nandawit.
