\v 56 Jamba but am…®n, ji da m…®kt…®mon ae kwen yo morap toŇč p…®ndagek kokwin tag…®si aŇč. Mani ab…®sok yo morap altoŇč uŇčun p…®ndagek kokwin nido tag…® d…®ma aŇč?‚ÄĚ
