\v 1 Yesu p…®ndak egakwan yoni morapm…® am…®n Telag…® Yut Madep dakon paret …®dapmon paretni yopgwit.
\v 2 Ae kaŇčakwan sakwabat k…®nda uŇčun yoni m…®ni, uŇčun da moneŇč g…®manjok bamor…® paret …®dapmon yopgut. \fig Sakwabat k…®nda paret yopgut|alt="Widow putting money" src="IB04114.tif" size="col" loc="Location" copy="Copyright" ref="21.2"\fig*
\v 3 \x - \xo 21:3 \xt 2Ko 8.12\x* Aban Yesu da yag…®t, ‚ÄúAsisi day…®sat, sakwabat yoni m…®ni on da am…®n morap da paret yopmaŇč uŇčun yapmaŇček moneŇč madepsi yopmaŇčdak.
\v 4 Am…®n morap uŇčun moneŇčni morapm…® taŇč yomaŇčakwa d…®war…® g…®n paret …®dapmon yopmaŇč. Mani on m…®Ňčat wadak wadaksi aŇček moneŇčni k…®si yopmaŇčdak. K…®l…® jap yumaŇč nosak moneŇčni d…® d…®ma taŇč …®maŇč.‚ÄĚ
\s1 Yesu da Telag…® Yut Madep tuw…®lni do yag…®t
